Return & Exchange Policy

Your satisfaction is our priority

Returns & Exchanges

We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy with your order, we offer hassle-free returns and exchanges within 7 days of delivery.

Conditions for Return

  • Product must be unused and in original packaging
  • All tags and labels must be intact
  • Return request must be made within 7 days of delivery
  • Product should not be damaged or altered

How to Return

  1. Contact us via WhatsApp at +923235063462
  2. Provide your order details and reason for return
  3. Our team will arrange pickup or guide you on return shipping
  4. Refund will be processed within 3-5 business days after receiving the item

Note: Return shipping charges may apply unless the product is defective or incorrect.

Size Guide

Find your perfect fit

How to Measure Your Wrist

Follow these simple steps to find your perfect bangle or bracelet size:

  1. Take a measuring tape or a piece of string
  2. Wrap it around your wrist at the widest point (just below the wrist bone)
  3. Make sure it's snug but not too tight
  4. Note the measurement in inches or centimeters

Standard Sizes

Size Wrist Measurement Bangle Size
Small (2.4) 6.5 - 7 inches 2.4 inches diameter
Medium (2.6) 7 - 7.5 inches 2.6 inches diameter
Large (2.8) 7.5 - 8 inches 2.8 inches diameter
Extra Large (2.10) 8 - 8.5 inches 2.10 inches diameter

Tip: If you're between sizes, we recommend going for the larger size for comfort. Contact us on WhatsApp for personalized sizing assistance!
